The paper proposes a new random graph model for community detection, which is a topic of interest in several sub-fields of computer science. The paper also discusses the performance of a triangle-counting algorithm for community detection in the proposed model, which suggests that the paper may belong to sub-categories related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), and network analysis (cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.NA).
